A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Mayor Allison Wilkerson; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Mayor Allison Wilkerson has long been recognized by the citizens of this state
3 for the vital role that she has played in leadership and her deep personal commitment to the
4 welfare of the citizens of Georgia; and
5 WHEREAS, Mayor Wilkerson is a lifelong resident of both Gwinnett County and the City
6 of Grayson; and
7 WHEREAS, a graduate of the 2001 Leadership Gwinnett Class, Mayor Wilkerson was
8 elected to her first term as a Grayson City Council member in 2002 and served the Grayson
9 community for twelve years; and
10 WHEREAS, in 2014, she was elected as the first female and second-generation mayor of the
11 city; and
12 WHEREAS, she selflessly serves on the school council board at Grayson Elementary School,
13 is president of District 3 on the Georgia Municipal Association’s Training Board, and is a
