14 recipient of the Servant Leadership Award from the Georgia Women’s Legislative Caucus;
15 and
16 WHEREAS, Mayor Wilkerson's significant organizational and leadership talents, remarkable
17 patience and diplomacy, keen sense of vision, and sensitivity to the needs of the citizens of
18 this state have earned her the respect and admiration of her community; and
19 WHEREAS, she is a person of magnanimous strengths with an unimpeachable reputation for
20 integrity, intelligence, fairness, and kindness; and
21 WHEREAS, Mayor Wilkerson has served with honor and distinction, and her vision and
22 unyielding commitment to the City of Grayson has set the standard for public service; and
23 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the outstanding accomplishments of this
24 remarkable and distinguished Georgian be appropriately recognized.
25 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
26 the members of this body recognize and commend Mayor Allison Wilkerson and extend the
27 most sincere best wishes for continued health and happiness.
28 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
29 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Mayor
30 Allison Wilkerson.
